Northam Platinum Says Worker Dies After Accident at Zondereinde Operation

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-06-03T06:41:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/northam-platinum-says-worker-dies-after-accident-at-zondereinde-operation.html
Northam Platinum Ltd. (NHM)  said a worker
who was injured in a May 27 accident during water-jet cleaning
operations at its Zondereinde mine has died. The company
commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  